# Stage 1: Build frontend with Node.js
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY frontend/package*.json ./
RUN npm ci && npm run build

# Stage 2: Poetry builder for Python dependencies
FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder

WORKDIR /build

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./
RUN pip install poetry && \
    poetry config virtualenvs.create true && \
    poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry export -f requirements.txt --without-hashes -o requirements.txt && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt

# Stage 3: Final runtime image
FROM python:3.12-slim

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && \
    useradd -m -u 1000 -s /bin/bash superset

COPY --from=frontend-builder /build/frontend/dist ./frontend/dist
COPY --chown=superset:superset --from=python-builder /usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages /usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages

COPY --chown=superset:superset . .

USER superset

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team@example.com" \
      description="Python analytics platform with React frontend"

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
